_:N0e7c87c2d7f745b3aabe43084462b2a6 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Air Vice-Marshal Mark Hunt was appointed Deputy Director General and Technical Director for the Defence Safety Authority on 18 December 2024.</p>\n\n<p>His previous Ministry of Defence roles include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Defence Equipment and Support Team Leader, Type Airworthiness Authority, Portfolio Head and Principal Engineer</li>\n  <li>Director of Ground Training (delivering the RAF’s education policy, governance and assurance for all 27 specialist disciplines)</li>\n  <li>Deputy Air Officer commanding No 22 Group</li>\n  <li>Commandant of the Defence School of Aeronautical Engineering</li>\n  <li>RAF Cosford’s Station Commander, Head of Establishment and Accountable Manager</li>\n  <li>Chief Air Engineer at RAF Brize Norton</li>\n</ul>\n" .
